reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars S5Max Laptop - A Powerhouse of Performance and Visuals
reviews.reviewText: I recently got the S5Max Laptop and it's been an absolute joy to use. The 16-inch Full HD IPS display is a standout feature, offering vibrant colors and sharp text that make everything from watching movies to browsing a pleasure. The screen's 93% screen-to-body ratio adds to its immersive experience.Performance-wise, it's a powerhouse. The Intel Celeron processor ensures smooth multitasking, and the 4GB DDR4 memory and 128GB EMMC storage are more than sufficient for daily tasks. The sound quality from the four stereo speakers is impressive, enhancing my gaming and movie-watching sessions.Another big plus is the 1-year Office-365 subscription, which is great for work and my kids' school assignments. The variety of ports and connectivity options like USB 3.0, Type-C, and dual-band Wi-Fi make it very user-friendly.Overall, the S5Max is a fantastic choice for anyone needing a reliable, high-performance laptop for both work and leisure. I highly recommend it!

reviews.reviewTitle: Great seller super fast delivery and a really good all round vfm laptop
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I waited over a month before submitting my review so I had a decent chance to evaluate it.It is my first windows 11 machine so it has taken a little time to get used to the new OS but that is no fault of the laptop itself which boots up really fast has a great battey life is really quiet, handles all processes I have tried on it really well.This week I have been doing a fair bit of video processing I am impressed with the rendering time and if watching online tv or video I have not experienced any buffering even in ultra HD.I was a little concerned about the US keyboard but uk format silicon cover is really easy to fit, doesnt fall off , keeps dirt out of the keys and may prevent damage should you accidentally splash the keyboard with anyhting.I am reaaly happy with my purchase at a great price of £307.I am not a gamer so can't vouch for its gaming capability but as a portable all round machine I thoroughly reccomend it.
